hkgmoji\" /> ，索下成隻腳板 (著住熱褲+除左襪) 就5份喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書妹企左成日，又想快d收工，所以收尾答應左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後帶左賣書妹去一條後行，佢除左隻鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，遞起一隻透到腳趾同腳板既襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。o個時已經有一陣好強烈既臭味飄緊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，聞到真係扯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到咁撚正，味度又咁強，緊係即刻開波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。賣書妹企左成日，d腳汗真係臭撚過鹹魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用個鼻又佢腳板一路掃，去到腳板心真係頂唔順，直頭黎一個濕吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我啜呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 賣書妹當堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左，但係好似又幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完臭腳板，最正既一刻黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，賣書妹剝左對襪， 陣鹹魚臭腳味全力散播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書妹企到腳支力，所以就郁郁下自己d腳趾黎放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。見到d腳趾咁性感<img src=\"/assets/fa