sets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，索下成隻腳板 (著住熱褲+除左襪) 就5份喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書妹企左成日，又想快d收工，所以收尾答應左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後帶左賣書妹去一條後行，佢除左隻鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，遞起一隻透到腳趾同腳板既襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。o個時已經有一陣好強烈既臭味飄緊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，聞到真係扯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到咁撚正，味度又咁強，緊係即刻開波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。賣書妹企左成日，d腳汗真係臭撚過鹹魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用個鼻又佢腳板一路掃，去到腳板心真係頂唔順，直頭黎一個濕吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我啜呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 賣書妹當堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左，但係好似又幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完臭腳板，最正既一刻黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，賣書妹剝左對襪， 陣鹹魚臭腳味全力散播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書妹企到腳支力，所以就郁郁下自己d腳趾黎放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。見到d腳趾咁性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，即刻將個鼻痴埋去，夾o係腳趾罅中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。用個鼻o係佢d腳趾罅到摸擦，擦左d老泥出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真係極大收獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後就係聞佢隻黃咁咁既臭腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著完襪隻腳板真係特別臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聞到腳板心汗位既味度真係食過返尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個賣書妹拉住我話一本一Q添啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3b88f424cd1579c351676022f13a8724ce29ce","tid":335071,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"8點鐘去到會唔會仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9833b2d8b3057c0e76c7ae902f771a8bd274d487","tid":335071,"uid":12008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8點鐘去到會唔會仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會"},{"pid":"c75cd1b81b678d50a1842894e9c07e5a39ab0aed","tid":335071,"uid":73737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:33:33.000Z","msg":"冇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7949bbf72503423b15df13e99bc535a8117309ae","tid":335071,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"上一頁黑色熱褲幾正<br />\n夠白淨"},{"pid":"97311412f7e231fe8d41d43a0cf44d71db17ba0e","tid":335071,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote